\"}],\" \",\"Riverwalk access tips included\"]}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/san-antonio-tx/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"San Antonio dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"$L29\",null,{\"city\":\"San Antonio\",\"state\":\"TX\"}]\n17:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"className\":\"city-insights-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2a\",null,{\"parks\":[{\"id\":\"ChIJlyaoHcuLXIYRVDKDQ0nJXa8\",\"name\":\"Alamo City Dog Trainers\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Alamo City Dog Trainers is a beloved pet store in San Antonio that consistently earns praise from pet owners. This facility stands out for being spacious play areas and friendly and caring staff and excellent customer service. Dog owners appreciate the attention to detail and the genuine care shown to every furry visitor. For more information, call (210) 679-1495.\",\"slug\":\"alamo-city-dog-trainers\",\"address\":\"314 Sherman\",\"street\":\"314 Sherman\",\"city\":\"San Antonio\",\"state\":\"TX\",\"zipCode\":\"78202\",\"full_address\":\"314 Sherman, San Antonio, TX 78202, USA\",\"latitude\":29.4338078,\"longitude\":-98.47407400000002,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJlyaoHcuLXIYRVDKDQ0nJXa8\",\"phone\":\"(210) 679-1495\",\"website\":\"http://www.alamocitydogtrainers.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":127,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Tuesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Wednesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Thursday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Friday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Saturday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Sunday\":\"Open 24 hours\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,